title: Elle UK font ID
content:
I'm trying to figure out what this bold font is from Elle UK magazine. Any ideas?

 ![](http://web.archive.org/web/20150414044002im_/http:/typophile.com/files/test_4897.jpg)

 ![](http://web.archive.org/web/20150414044002im_/http:/typophile.com/files/test2_6314.jpg)
author: jsum

comments.content: According to [Akira](http://web.archive.org/web/20150414044002/http:/www.myfonts.com/WhatTheFont/forum/case/590205), should be [Domaine](http://web.archive.org/web/20150414044002/http:/typophile.com/wiki/https%3A/%252Fklim.co.nz/blog/tag/domaine) by KLIM Kris Sowersby, not released yet.
